OL,3,CPolice Ombudsman apologises to staff
OL,4,Cafter data leak
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's police watchdog has
OL,7,Fapologised to its staff after their
OL,8,Fdetails were inadvertently shared with
OL,9,Falmost two dozen job applicants.
OL,11,FThe data leak at the Police Ombudsman
OL,12,Ffor Northern Ireland involved the
OL,13,Fdetails of 160 current and former
OL,14,Femployees.
