OL,3,CPolice Ombudsman apologises to staff
OL,4,Cafter data leak
OL,6,FThe information, which contained
OL,7,Fdetails of the workforce in May 2022,
OL,8,Fwas contained in a three-page Word
OL,9,Fdocument that was released to 22
OL,10,Fpeople who had been invited to
OL,11,Fparticipate in an interview as part of
OL,12,Fa recruitment exercise.
OL,14,FThe document contained the forename
OL,15,Finitial and surname of all members of
OL,16,Fstaff employed as of May 2022. It also
OL,17,Flisted the service area or team in
OL,18,Fwhich the employees worked and if a
OL,19,Fmember of staff was part-time, agency,
OL,20,Fcontracted or seconded.
