OL,3,CPolice Ombudsman apologises to staff
OL,4,Cafter data leak
OL,6,FInformation on staff movements,
OL,7,Fincluding those who had resigned, were
OL,8,Fdue to retire, were on career breaks,
OL,9,Fmoving between teams, or new starts,
OL,10,Fwas also included. Some forenames were
OL,11,Fincluded in that data set.
OL,13,FA spokesman for the Police Ombudsman's
OL,14,Foffice said no other personal
OL,15,Finformation was contained in the
OL,16,Fleaked document.
OL,18,F"The office has taken immediate action
OL,19,Fto mitigate the breach, including
OL,20,Fcontacting those who received the
OL,21,Fdocument in error," he said.
