OL,3,CPolice Ombudsman apologises to staff
OL,4,Cafter data leak
OL,6,F"To date, 20 of the 22 individuals
OL,7,Fhave confirmed that they have deleted
OL,8,Fthe email and associated documentation.
OL,10,F"We have apologised unreservedly to
OL,11,Four current staff for the error, which
OL,12,Fshould not have happened, and are also
OL,13,Fcontacting former staff whose details
OL,14,Fare included in the document.
OL,16,F"In total 160 current and former staff
OL,17,Fare affected.
